Notes for a silo reservation system for pools



Procedural Description
----------------------

Add the silo information 

  * is the silo ro/rw?  If rw continue
  * does the silo have
  * determine the partition the silo filesystem exists on
  * what outstanding reservations are on that filesystem? (remove those that have timed out - two hours?)
 




Functional Description
----------------------

SilosReservation:

   ob = SiloReservation.new(*Silos) 
   ob.silo
   ob.release 


Silos:

silo.rw?
silo.root_filesystem



